name: "Laughing, Anger, Joy"
description:
"Something will remain, I can see that you came in yesterday... we'll build castles in the air that will fall down like blue water..."

Video Montage - 2021.

This is the third "mini video" of a series of visual stories involving the "girl in the red dress" and myself, Lautaro Quiroga, as a character of this metaverse.

Girl in the red dress: Camila Pláate.
